Hundreds of Zambians have fled their border villages since the
incursions by armed men believed to be Angolans started last year.
</P>
<P>
Last week an armed Angolan soldier was captured in Zambezi
District of Zambia after an exchange of fire with Zambian army in
which a Zambian soldier and two civilians were injured. 
