<HEADLINE> New Chinese-English Dictionary Published </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 6 (Xinhua) -- A conference was held today here to
mark the recent issue of the Xinhua Chinese-English Dictionary.
</P>
