<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, June 6 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait Stock Exchange index
closed at 1,425.4 points Tuesday, down 12.1 points from Monday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was 5.38 million Kuwaiti dinars (17.75 million U.
S. dollars) as 22.42 million shares were traded in 609 deals.
</P>
