institutes of higher learning in China. It has trained 100,000
students including some experts well-known both at home and abroad.
</P>
<P>
In April, the Nanjing Railway Medical College, Nanjing
Transport Training School and Nanjing Geology School merged with
the old Southeast China University, making it into a comprehensive
university with engineering as its mainstay.  
