deliberate," the spokesman said.
</P>
<P>
Australian Foreign Minister Alexander Downer had discussed the
request with Ulufa'alu at length, the spokesman said.
</P>
<P>
"He (Howard) said that it was something that given the racial
tension in the Solomons that they had to find their own solution,"
the spokesman said. 
