origin, Franklin Chang, who traveled in one of the space ferries.
</P>
<P>
Director of Civil Aviation, Miguel Ramos, considered that the
country will be benefited with NASA missions in different ways, as
photographs taken will be of use for diverse projects and some
experiments in the agricultural sector," Experts from Costa Rica
University and Agricultural School of the Humid Tropic (EARTH)
will participate in these experiments. "This will create programs
of scientific cooperation between these institutions, added Ramos,
