forces, while also giving all European countries a "100%
guarantee" of security with the support of their American partner.
</P>
<P>
In the Russia-U.S. summit in Moscow at the last weekend, Putin
refused to accept the amendment of the anti- ballistic missile
treaty which Clinton needs to go ahead with the planned U.S. anti-
missile shield. 
